    "steps": [
        {
            "stepNo": 1,
            "content": "把雞腿肉切塊狀,放入姜泥,醬油及黑胡椒,拌勻靜置20分",
            "imageUrl": "http://pic.daydaycook.com/production/images/20160512/2ca0d4d6-4634-4ace-85bc-e31dc62cbafd",
            "languageId": null
        },
        {
            "stepNo": 2,
            "content": "加入蛋清及馬鈴薯澱粉用手拌勻",
            "imageUrl": "http://pic.daydaycook.com/production/images/20160512/4949c524-3259-4b73-8d7e-1a329001ef86",
            "languageId": null
        },
        {
            "stepNo": 3,
            "content": "把大蔥切絲, 蒜瓣切1/2",
            "imageUrl": "http://pic.daydaycook.com/production/images/20160512/3c1c50e5-0334-4582-960d-832150c5dbfc",
            "languageId": null
        },
        {
            "stepNo": 4,
            "content": "準備小鍋,倒入125毫升的油,加熱,放入大蒜及蔥絲炸金黃色, 撈起備用",
            "imageUrl": "http://pic.daydaycook.com/production/images/20160512/3db36dc3-369e-4c19-9aeb-6be71aa4d32f",
            "languageId": null
        },
        {
            "stepNo": 5,
            "content": "接著取用適量熱油倒入辣椒麵,降溫後過濾辣椒麵,保存辣油備用",
            "imageUrl": "http://pic.daydaycook.com/production/images/20160512/3aa5e229-1cad-40a0-b049-677b59102bce",
            "languageId": null
        },
        {
            "stepNo": 6,
            "content": "準備炸鍋倒入1000毫升的油,大火加熱約4分鐘,轉中火,把雞肉放入油鍋內,不停翻拌油鍋內的雞肉,大約炸五分鐘,撈起,熄火",
            "imageUrl": "http://pic.daydaycook.com/production/images/20160512/b262dee0-1f6e-40c2-befb-39db9faf7a91",
            "languageId": null
        },
        {
            "stepNo": 7,
            "content": "把紅綠辣椒切絲備用",
            "imageUrl": "http://pic.daydaycook.com/production/images/20160512/4292a844-b1da-4b78-b027-0195ba7bb9eb",
            "languageId": null
        },
        {
            "stepNo": 8,
            "content": "準備小碗放入醬油,玉米糖漿,水,白醋及馬鈴薯澱粉拌勻備用",
            "imageUrl": "http://pic.daydaycook.com/production/images/20160512/8ed4c467-42e6-429f-b588-4dfd4f907074",
            "languageId": null
        },
        {
            "stepNo": 9,
            "content": "取一個炒鍋,放入自製辣油加熱,放入紅綠辣椒絲,洋蔥丁,蔥末,乾辣椒,大火爆炒2~3分,加入拌好的酸甜醬汁熬煮20~30秒後熄火",
            "imageUrl": "http://pic.daydaycook.com/production/images/20160512/11bffaef-5682-4a25-9d0f-71f8efdac24d",
            "languageId": null
        },
        {
            "stepNo": 10,
            "content": "把炸過的雞塊再次回鍋炸約3~5分鐘直到淺棕色後撈起瀝乾",
            "imageUrl": "http://pic.daydaycook.com/production/images/20160512/e5758494-abec-4582-86bb-a8888e733c2c",
            "languageId": null
        },
        {
            "stepNo": 11,
            "content": "把炸好的雞塊放入步驟（4）鍋內加熱,使雞塊均勻裹上醬汁,放入炸過的蔥絲,大蒜,香油及白芝麻,拌勻裝盤",
            "imageUrl": "http://pic.daydaycook.com/production/images/20160512/f7e415a2-34ee-42da-8aba-2a9768daf853",
            "languageId": null
        }
